mer om denne saken i Adresseavisen fredag. H\u00f8r ogs\u00e5 innslag p\u00e5 RadioAdressa i dag klokken 16.15."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "809bf8e76905acd4f2491d29c0947b0b4bc95e3d301ee20c555d96cd984909c7"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-05-01T10:22:49.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Vanvikan skole stenger en del av skoleomr\u00e5det og innf\u00f8rer t\u00f8ffe regler, etter at flere skolebarn skal ha v\u00e6rt med p\u00e5 en voldelig Ringens Herre-lek."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1112023.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/ver2%20atter-soldater"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/a2f30bb60391001c3eac3ab67b1d4d4df3b35221.jpg?59070c79"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Skoleomr\u00e5de stengt etter brutal Ringenes Herre-lek -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "a2f30bb60391001c3eac3ab67b1d4d4df3b35221"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "education"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["v\u00e5pen", "rektor kaller", "rektor", "skole", "stengt", "leken", "skoleomr\u00e5de stengt", "brev"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["ringens herre", "adresseavisen", "ringenes herre", "hjemmelagede", "vanvikan", "radioadressa"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": "erik solberg"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1112023.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/ver2%20atter-soldater"}, {"field": "og-local